ee.bpw.dhx.model

Class DhxRecipient

  • java.lang.Object
    • ee.bpw.dhx.model.DhxRecipient

  • public class DhxRecipient
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents recipient of the document. Helps to easily define to whom the document is really sent. Recipient might be not obvious if document is sent to representee. This class contains representees data if document is sent to representee and direct reciever data if it is sent directly, not to representee.
    Author:
    Aleksei Kokarev
